# Calculate RMSE (Root Mean Squared Error)
# RMSE is typically calculated for actual vs. predicted values, not their difference directly.
# If we want RMSE of the difference, it's essentially the standard deviation of the difference
# if the mean difference is zero, or more generally, sqrt(mean_squared_error(actual, predicted)).
# Here, we'll calculate RMSE as sqrt(mean(difference^2)).
rmse_rt_diff = np.sqrt(mean_squared_error(
    cnm_predictions_df['actual_rt_ms'],
    cnm_predictions_df['predicted_rt_ms']
))

